      (a) A tool badge appears in the chat response (shows filesystem/
          list_directory or similar)
      (b) docker logs mcpo 2>&1 | grep "Calling endpoint" shows a
          list_directory or list_directory_with_sizes entry
    FAIL indicators:
      - No badge (model answered without calling tool)
      - Memory tool badge appears (wrong tool selected)
    If FAIL: confirm wall-e model is selected (not qwen2.5), confirm Native
    mode is active, confirm filesystem tool is toggled ON in the chat.

  Test 2 — Memory write with file verification:
    Say: "Remember that my test phrase is banana"
    PASS criteria:
      (a) A tool badge appears (memory/create_entities or add_observations)
